OL,3,CTeenager appears in court accused of
OL,4,Carson attack that left girl, 15, dead
OL,6,FA teenager has appeared in court
OL,7,Faccused of killing a 15-year-old girl
OL,8,Fin an arson attack on a block of flats
OL,9,Fthree years ago.
OL,11,FTiffany Regis, 15, died from smoke
OL,12,Finhalation after a fire on Tollgate
OL,13,FRoad, Beckton, east London, on April 6
OL,14,F2023.
OL,16,FFive other people at the address were
OL,17,Finjured but later discharged from
OL,18,Fhospital.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
