OL,3,CTeenager appears in court accused of
OL,4,Carson attack that left girl, 15, dead
OL,6,FA boy, who was aged 13 at the time of
OL,7,Fthe incident, was charged with her
OL,8,Fmanslaughter, arson and arson with
OL,9,Frecklessness as to whether life was
OL,10,Fendangered.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday, the youth, who is now aged
OL,13,F16, appeared at the Old Bailey before
OL,14,FJudge Mark Lucraft KC.
OL,16,FThe judge set a trial lasting up to
OL,17,Ffour weeks at the Old Bailey from
OL,18,FNovember 23.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/3
