OL,3,CTeenager appears in court accused of
OL,4,Carson attack that left girl, 15, dead
OL,6,FThe defendant, who is on conditional
OL,7,Fbail, was not asked to enter pleas to
OL,8,Fthe charges against him.
OL,10,FA further hearing will take place on
OL,11,FJune 9.
